cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CE, cs.HC, cs.SI 

This paper is primarily focused on developing a method for off-policy evaluation in reinforcement learning, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the application of this method in healthcare (cs.HC) and education (cs.CE) domains, which suggests that it may be relevant to those sub-categories as well. Additionally, the paper proposes a hybrid human-AI system, which could be considered under the sub-category of social and information sciences (cs.SI).
